-- Mexico's Ixe Grupo Financiero Says It's Studying Merger With Rival Banorte
-- B y   A n d r e s   R .   M a r t i n e z
-- 2010-10-19T20:15:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-19/mexico-s-ixe-grupo-financiero-says-it-s-studying-merger-with-rival-banorte.html
Ixe Grupo Financiero SAB said it may
merge or integrate operations with Grupo Financiero Banorte SAB.  The companies have a non-binding agreement to discuss a
merger, Ixe said in a statement to the Mexican stock exchange.  Banorte said in a separate statement that Ixe may become
part of its operations.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andres R. Martinez at 
 amartinez28@bloomberg.net  